"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?1/44/1732?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Having twins (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?33/63/34805?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Deciding to breastfeed (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?17/25/17813?source=see_link\">",
